Package org.hms.services.staffmanagement

Class Staff

java.lang.Object
org.hms.entities.AbstractTableEntry
org.hms.services.staffmanagement.Staff
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Staff extends AbstractTableEntry
The Staff class represents a staff member with relevant details, such as staff ID, age, name, role, status, and gender. It is an extension of the AbstractTableEntry and includes additional properties specific to the staff.
